title: Strubiny, Nowy Dwór Mazowiecki County
data: Strubiny [struˈbinɨ] is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Zakroczym, within Nowy Dwór County, Masovian Voivodeship, in east-central Poland.[1] It lies approximately 6 kilometres (4 mi) north of Zakroczym, 8 km (5 mi) north-west of Nowy Dwór Mazowiecki, and 40 km (25 mi) north-west of Warsaw.
